---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6 relative z-10 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">
                EXPERIENCIA <span class="text-[#00D9FF] glow-text">10/10</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/50 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">
                No es solo otro juego de palabras. Es un desafío visual y mental diseñado para los
                que no se conforman con lo básico.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <div
                class="group relative bg-[#0A1628]/40 border border-white/5 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#00D9FF]/40 hover:-translate-y-4"
            >
                <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/assets/apps/lexi-crash/screenshot_2.webp"
                        alt="Modo Crash"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0A1628] via-[#0A1628]/20 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-6 left-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#00D9FF] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#00D9FF]/40"
                    >
                        <Icon name="mdi:lightning-bolt" class="w-8 h-8 text-black" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-10 relative mt-[-60px]">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase text-[#00D9FF]">
                        Adrenalina Pura
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
                        Forma palabras bajo presión. Las letras no esperan. Despeja el tablero antes
                        de que el caos te supere.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-[#0A1628]/40 border border-white/5 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#FFBB00]/40 hover:-translate-y-4"
            >
                <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/assets/apps/lexi-crash/screenshot_3.webp"
                        alt="Modo Relax"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0A1628] via-[#0A1628]/20 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-6 left-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#FFBB00] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#FFBB00]/40"
                    >
                        <Icon name="mdi:weather-sunny" class="w-8 h-8 text-black" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-10 relative mt-[-60px]">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase text-[#FFBB00]">
                        Maestría Mental
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
                        Tómate tu tiempo. Sin presión visual, solo tú y el tablero. Encuentra las
                        combinaciones más valiosas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-[#0A1628]/40 border border-white/5 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:border-[#FF4500]/40 hover:-translate-y-4"
            >
                <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/assets/apps/lexi-crash/screenshot_1.webp"
                        alt="Reto Diario"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0A1628] via-[#0A1628]/20 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-6 left-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#FF4500] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#FF4500]/40"
                    >
                        <Icon name="mdi:calendar-star" class="w-8 h-8 text-black" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-10 relative mt-[-60px]">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase text-[#FF4500]">Reto Global</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
                        Una palabra secreta al día. Todo el mundo compite por ser el más rápido.
                        ¿Podrás liderar el ranking?
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .glow-text {
        text-shadow:
            0 0 30px rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.8),
            0 0 60px rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.4);
    }
</style>
